            "value": "<p><strong>Usage</strong> held in 1 hand</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span>&nbsp;Strike</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Blight bombs contain volatile toxic chemicals that rot flesh. A blight bomb deals the listed poison damage, persistent poison damage, and splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.</p>\n<p>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 poison damage, 3d4 persistent poison damage, and 3 poison splash damage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
